Docker & Kubernetes SRE Engineering Handbook 

This section is a production-focused guide for Senior Site Reliability Engineers (SREs) covering Docker, orchestration,
Kubernetes, networking, deployments, debugging, and real-world incident response.

It is designed to take you from fundamentals → production architecture → cloud-native systems (AWS EKS).

1. Modern Containerized Architecture (SRE View)

Modern distributed systems follow this pipeline:

Application Code
↓
Docker Image
↓
